SUMMARY:Webinar: Stress and Burnout
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Stress and burnout are more than workplace challengesthey sign
 ificantly impact mental health. This seminar explores how chronic stress c
 ontributes to emotional exhaustion and reduced cognitive functioning. Lear
 n to recognize early warning signs\, understand the mindbody connection\, 
 and apply practical strategies to protect mental well-being\, build resili
 ence\, and prevent burnout. Presented by Bay Care and UHC Onsite Nurse Lia
 ison. This webinar does count toward your wellness incentive benefit - 100
   quarter. Registration : 6.17.26 Stress and Burnout (https:events.teams.m
