SUMMARY:Studio55: Collage Explorations
LOCATION:522 N Howard Ave Tampa \, FL 33606 United States
DESCRIPTION:Ready to fall under the spell of collage? Join us for an eight
 -week course\, where well explore the wonderfully scrappy\, layered\, stor
 y-filled world of collage art. Each week\, well dive into hands-on exercis
 es that build your skills. Think composition and color but taught the fun 
 way. Think layering and mixed media but with zero pressure and lots of let
 s just see what happens. Youll work with a mix of found materials\, handma
 de papers\, ephemera\, textures\, paints\, and anything else you feel like
  cutting up. Thursdays\, Jun 18 - Aug 6  1:004:00 PM (8 classes) Ages 55  
 Beginner Level This class located at the Shanna and Bryan Glazer JCC in Ta
 mpa\, FL \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/188706
